---

<div class="py-24 bg-charcoal relative overflow-hidden" id="keunggulan">
    <!-- Background Map/Globe Effect -->
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none bg-[url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ec/World_map_blank_without_borders.svg')] bg-cover bg-center mix-blend-overlay"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="px-4 md:px-10 lg:px-40 flex justify-center relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col max-w-[1200px] w-full gap-16">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4"
                data-aos="fade-up"
            >
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 px-4 py-1.5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm"
                >
                    <span
                        class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"
                    ></span>
                    <span
                        class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest"
                        >Kenapa Memilih Kami?</span
                    >
                </div>
                <h2
                    class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-black"
                >
                    Standar Industri <span
                        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent"
                        >Profesional</span
                    >
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl">
                    Kami tidak hanya sekedar mengelas, tapi memberikan solusi
                    konstruksi yang aman, estetis, dan tahan lama untuk properti
                    Anda.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <!-- Point 1 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 group"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="0"
                >
                    <div
                        class="size-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-light to-charcoal border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center relative group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-xl"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-xl opacity-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 rounded-full"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary relative z-10"
                            >verified</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-2">
                            Material SNI
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Hanya menggunakan besi & baja bersertifikat SNI yang
                            terjamin kekuatannya.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Point 2 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 group"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="100"
                >
                    <div
                        class="size-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-light to-charcoal border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center relative group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-xl"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 rounded-full"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary relative z-10"
                            >workspace_premium</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-2">
                            Garansi 6 Bulan
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Jaminan perbaikan gratis jika ada kerusakan pada
                            hasil pengelasan kami.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Point 3 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 group"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="200"
                >
                    <div
                        class="size-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-light to-charcoal border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center relative group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-xl"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 rounded-full"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary relative z-10"
                            >engineering</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-2">
                            20+ Tahun Pengalaman
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Dikerjakan oleh tenaga ahli yang telah mengerjakan
                            ratusan proyek konstruksi.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Point 4 -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 group"
                    data-aos="fade-up"
                    data-aos-delay="300"
                >
                    <div
                        class="size-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-light to-charcoal border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center relative group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-xl"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 rounded-full"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary relative z-10"
                            >payments</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-2">
                            Harga Transparan
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Rincian biaya jelas di awal. Tanpa biaya
                            tersembunyi. Survey & Konsultasi Gratis.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
